      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>I'm not looking for a hotline. I just... I've spent years building this, and now it's just dust. I look at my life and I don't even see a person anymore, just a debt. It feels like there's no point in even trying to climb back up when the math just doesn't work. It's like the universe is telling me it's over. Does it even make sense to try and fight something that's already decided?",
